data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and charm in this inviting 3BR, 2.5Bath home! All 3 bedrooms are conveniently located upstairs. Step outside to a delightful deck, with a pergola outside the fenced-in yard--an ideal setting for relaxation or outdoor gatherings!Situated at the end of a cul-de sac, this home has a trail to Baxter Bog and is close to Base and hospitals like Providence!Sellers paid for professional replacement of carpet for the entire upstairs so you can enjoy a brand new one!
